{"tid":2235201,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MV風格太雷同　Lizzy開酸宇宙少女「希望可以超越橙子焦糖唷」","createTime":"2020-10-08T13:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T04:06:57.000Z","uid":74065,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3cab2a7fc8cd93c87d8aebc562c2c740b029fee4","tid":2235201,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:04:03.000Z","msg":"宇宙少女是STARSHIP娛樂與大陸樂華娛樂共同推出的13人女團，靠著清純、甜美的音樂風格擄獲了大批歌迷的心，近日成員秀彬、Luda、夏天與多榮一同組成子團「WJSN CHOCOME」，新歌《Hmph》才推出一天，竟引來前輩「After School」的Lizzy開酸，引起許多網友討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5193/d5193359.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5193%2Fd5193359.jpg&h=ec209725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宇宙少女推出子團。（圖／翻攝自宇宙少女IG）<br />\n<br />\n宇宙少女子團「WJSN CHOCOME」在7日發表新歌《Hmph》，洗腦的曲調與復古的風格受到許多網友討論，成員秀彬、Luda、夏天與多榮在MV穿上浮誇著紗裙、洋裝，還在頭上戴著超大的蝴蝶結，搭配搞怪的舞步，讓影片才公開一天，就累積了超過20萬次觀看。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5193/d5193360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5193%2Fd5193360.jpg&h=cae2b0cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宇宙少女推出子團。（圖／翻攝自宇宙少女IG）<br />\n<br />\n只不過，「WJSN CHOCOME」復古感十足的MV，竟引來「After School」的Lizzy開酸，認為整體風格與「After School」子團「橙子焦糖」太過雷同，在自己的Instagram發文，貼出《Hmph》MV截圖表示「希望宇宙少女能夠超越橙子焦糖，但是MV中的概念跟橙子焦糖有很多相似的地方」，最後喊話隊友「Raina、NANA、Lizzy讚」，目前該則貼文已被刪除。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5193/5193355.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5193%2F5193355.jpg&h=43b3a8a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lizzy在Instagram開酸。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n然而，Lizzy開酸的貼文公開後，也隨即在網路上發酵，掀起正反兩派網友激戰，部分酸民認同Lizzy，表示「明顯抄襲，看不出來的是真傻子」、「這首歌真的非常橙子焦糖」，另外也有歌迷表達了對宇宙少女的支持，坦言「復古曲風誰都可以創作，又不是只有橙子焦糖可以」、「Lizzy太嗆了吧」，意外引起熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5193/d5193357.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5193%2Fd5193357.jpg&h=f9aa8517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5193/d5193356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5193%2Fd5193356.jpg&h=35008589&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲橙子焦糖是許多樂迷心中的經典女團。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RGnLdUJbYmQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRGnLdUJbYmQ&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrwbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=a4ccf65b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RGnLdUJbYmQ</a><br />\n<br />\n過氣老女人 唔怪得咁多年都冇幾隊試玩哩隻風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf454644169bb8478350c8b8e33527827c96db8","tid":2235201,"uid":256952,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:04:44.000Z","msg":"宇宙少女吹大左"},{"pid":"7a1e1398f0675f7f553452d7bef9f92241798d3f","tid":2235201,"uid":219225,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"izone吊打orange caramel"},{"pid":"04ee858ec05e9af4094ed4a43d59bdd9d1800eb6","tid":2235201,"uid":74065,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"7a1e1398f0675f7f553452d7bef9f92241798d3f","tid":2235201,"uid":219225,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"izone吊打orange caramel"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:07:40.000Z","msg":"關IZONE咩事=="},{"pid":"5653ad57af1b45684336fbb4241b587831fb7919","tid":2235201,"uid":60256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:10:39.000Z","msg":"又一抄團"},{"pid":"80a14ff8996d6d7b56a2fee977f9576488b88e11","tid":2235201,"uid":74065,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"5653ad57af1b45684336fbb4241b587831fb7919","tid":2235201,"uid":60256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:10:39.000Z","msg":"又一抄團"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Td6X3yw.jpg\" data-thumbnai